<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MC Build Network</title>

```
<style>
    *{
        margin:0;
        padding:0;
        box-sizing:border-box;
        font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
    }

    body{
        background:#0f172a;
        color:white;
    }

    header{
        background:#111827;
        padding:20px;
        text-align:center;
        border-bottom:3px solid #00ff88;
    }

    header h1{
        color:#00ff88;
        font-size:3rem;
    }

    nav{
        margin-top:10px;
    }

    nav a{
        color:white;
        text-decoration:none;
        margin:0 15px;
        font-weight:bold;
    }

    .hero{
        text-align:center;
        padding:80px 20px;
    }

    .hero h2{
        font-size:2.5rem;
        margin-bottom:15px;
    }

    .server-ip{
        background:#1e293b;
        display:inline-block;
        padding:15px 25px;
        border-radius:10px;
        margin-top:20px;
        font-size:1.2rem;
    }

    .ranks{
        padding:50px 20px;
        text-align:center;
    }

    .rank-container{
        display:flex;
        flex-wrap:wrap;
        justify-content:center;
        gap:20px;
    }

    .rank{
        background:#1e293b;
        width:280px;
        padding:20px;
        border-radius:15px;
        transition:0.3s;
    }

    .rank:hover{
        transform:translateY(-5px);
    }

    .rank h3{
        color:#00ff88;
        margin-bottom:10px;
    }

    .price{
        font-size:2rem;
        margin:15px 0;
    }

    .buy-btn{
        display:inline-block;
        padding:12px 20px;
        background:#00ff88;
        color:black;
        text-decoration:none;
        border-radius:8px;
        font-weight:bold;
    }

    .payment{
        text-align:center;
        padding:50px 20px;
    }

    .upi-box{
        background:#1e293b;
        display:inline-block;
        padding:20px;
        border-radius:15px;
        margin-top:20px;
    }

    .form-section{
        text-align:center;
        padding:50px 20px;
    }

    form{
        max-width:500px;
        margin:auto;
    }

    input, select{
        width:100%;
        padding:12px;
        margin:10px 0;
        border:none;
        border-radius:8px;
    }

    button{
        background:#00ff88;
        border:none;
        padding:12px 20px;
        border-radius:8px;
        font-weight:bold;
        cursor:pointer;
    }

    footer{
        background:#111827;
        text-align:center;
        padding:20px;
        margin-top:50px;
    }
</style>
```

</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>MC BUILD NETWORK</h1>
    <nav>
        <a href="#home">Home</a>
        <a href="#store">Store</a>
        <a href="#payment">Payment</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero" id="home">
    <h2>Welcome to MC Build Network</h2>
    <p>Best Minecraft Survival & Lifesteal Experience</p>

```
<div class="server-ip">
    Server IP: play.mcbuild.xyz
</div>
```

</section>

<section class="ranks" id="store">
    <h2>Server Store</h2>
    <br>

```
<div class="rank-container">

    <div class="rank">
        <h3>VIP Rank</h3>
        <p>Special Commands</p>
        <p>Colored Chat</p>
        <div class="price">₹49</div>
        <a href="#payment" class="buy-btn">Buy Now</a>
    </div>

    <div class="rank">
        <h3>TITAN Rank</h3>
        <p>Exclusive Kit</p>
        <p>Extra Homes</p>
        <div class="price">₹99</div>
        <a href="#payment" class="buy-btn">Buy Now</a>
    </div>

    <div class="rank">
        <h3>GOD Rank</h3>
        <p>All Titan Perks</p>
        <p>Premium Features</p>
        <div class="price">₹199</div>
        <a href="#payment" class="buy-btn">Buy Now</a>
    </div>

</div>
```

</section>

<section class="payment" id="payment">
    <h2>UPI Payment</h2>

```
<div class="upi-box">
    <h3>UPI ID</h3>
    <p>7300908683@upi</p>

    <br>

    <p>
        Scan QR from your UPI app or send payment to the UPI ID above.
    </p>
</div>
```

</section>

<section class="form-section">
    <h2>Purchase Form</h2>

```
<form>
    <input type="text" placeholder="Minecraft Username" required>

    <select required>
        <option>Select Rank</option>
        <option>VIP</option>
        <option>TITAN</option>
        <option>GOD</option>
    </select>

    <input type="text" placeholder="UPI Transaction ID" required>

    <button type="submit">Submit Purchase</button>
</form>
```

</section>

<footer>
    © 2026 MC Build Network
</footer>

</body>
</html>
